-- CIBC Sets Three-Year Target of C$3 Billion Annual Profit for Consumer Bank
-- B y   D a v i d   S c a n l a n
-- 2010-09-30T18:14:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-30/cibc-sets-three-year-target-of-c-3-billion-annual-profit-for-consumer-bank.html
Canadian Imperial Bank of Commerce
set a three-year target of posting a C$3 billion ($2.9 billion)
annual profit at its consumer bank. The Toronto-based lender
released the target in slides at an investor presentation today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
